# n8n Environment Variables - Railway Configuration

Copy these to **Railway** → **n8n service** → **Variables**

## Required Variables

```bash
# Appwrite Integration
APPWRITE_ENDPOINT=https://fra.cloud.appwrite.io/v1
APPWRITE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id
APPWRITE_DATABASE_ID=your-database-id
APPWRITE_API_KEY=your-appwrite-api-key

# Multi-LLM Engine
MULTI_LLM_ENGINE_URL=https://your-function.fra.appwrite.run

# OpenRouter API (for Qwen, Mistral, DeepSeek, Llama - FREE models)
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your-openrouter-api-key

# Google Drive Folder IDs
GOOGLE_DRIVE_PRD_FOLDER_ID=your-folder-id
GOOGLE_DRIVE_KNOWLEDGE_FOLDER_ID=your-folder-id
GOOGLE_DRIVE_CONTENT_FOLDER_ID=your-folder-id
GOOGLE_DRIVE_LEDGER_FOLDER_ID=your-folder-id

# Google Sheets
GOOGLE_SHEETS_LEDGER_ID=your-ledger-spreadsheet-id

# Human Layer (HITL Approvals)
HUMANLAYER_API_KEY=your-humanlayer-api-key
FOUNDER_PHONE=+254700000000

# Webhook Base URL (auto-set by n8n usually)
N8N_WEBHOOK_URL=https://your-n8n.railway.app
```

## Optional Variables

```bash
# M-Pesa (if using STK Push)
MPESA_ACCESS_TOKEN=your-token
MPESA_SHORTCODE=174379
MPESA_PASSWORD=your-password

# Skill Workflow IDs (for Execute Workflow nodes)
SKILL_PRD_GENERATOR_ID=your-workflow-id
SKILL_SHENG_NLP_ID=your-workflow-id
SKILL_LEDGER_ID=your-workflow-id
```

## How to Get Folder IDs

1. Open Google Drive
2. Navigate to or create folder `/Fikanova/PRDs`
3. Copy the ID from URL: `drive.google.com/drive/folders/FOLDER_ID_HERE`
4. Repeat for Knowledge, Content, Ledger folders

## Credentials to Configure in n8n UI

| Credential | Type | How to Get |
|------------|------|------------|
| Google Gemini API | API Key | [Google AI Studio](https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey) |
| Google Drive OAuth2 | OAuth | n8n → Credentials → Add → Google Drive |
| Google Sheets OAuth2 | OAuth | n8n → Credentials → Add → Google Sheets |
| HubSpot API | API Key | HubSpot → Settings → Private Apps |
